{"product_id":"hej-organic-glow-drops-14ml","title":"HEJ Organic Glow Drops 14ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eGlow Drops make your complexion shine and are the perfect finish for every look - whether with or without make-up. Compatible with every product, but can also shine all on its own. Niacinamide helps refine your pores.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eGlowy finish or spot highlights\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eEven skin texture thanks to niacinamide\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCan be used for face and body\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSuitable for all skin types \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e100% fragrance free  \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eMix 3-5 drops with your care or foundation. For that extra glow you can also apply directly to the skin. Add highlights to your cheeks or eyelids.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua (Water), Glycerin, Neopentyl Glycol Dicaprylate\/Dicaprate, Tridecyl Trimellitate, Dicaprylyl Ether, CI 77891 (Titanium Dioxide), Hydroxypropyl Starch, Glyceryl Stearate SE, Synthetic Flourphlogopite, Mica, Niacinamide, Tocopherol, Citrullus Lanatus Fruit Extract, Phenoxyethanol, Oryza Sativa Starch, Sodium Stearoyl Glutamate, Xanthan Gum, Sodium Acrylates Copolymer, Ethylhexyglycerin, CI 77492 (Iron Oxides), CI 77491 (Iron Oxides), Citric Acid, Lecithin, Tocopheryl Acetate, Tin Oxide, Sodium Citrate\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Hej","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50905862439239,"sku":null,"price":11.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hej-organi